    "description_long": "This is a small recreational motorboat with a compact cabin and a prominent red roof. The hull is painted in blue and white stripes, with a red accent along the bottom edge. The boat features a front deck with a wooden finish, side railings for safety, and a small chimney or exhaust pipe on the roof. Windows wrap around the cabin, providing visibility from all sides, and there is an anchor symbol painted on one side. The rear of the boat has an open deck area with a propeller and rudder visible beneath the stern.",
